{"tid":2258824,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"二條友住 煮咩最方便","createTime":"2020-10-26T10:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T17:38:02.000Z","uid":115,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fea3ed86a6a6ff6dc7a6157c602d25cde8dc5aa5","tid":2258824,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"成日撚煮 咖哩 or 日式牛飯<br />\n雖然方便又好味，但係有點厭<br />\n<br />\n醬汁：<br />\n1. S&amp;B 咖哩磚<br />\n2. 日本醬油，味琳<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n二個醬汁一撚樣煮都得<br />\n<br />\n洋蔥<br />\n薯仔<br />\n紅蘿蔔<br />\n青椒<br />\n蘑菇<br />\n自己鍾意嘅肉類<br />\n自己鍾意嘅材料<br />\n<br />\n所有材料放哂落鑊<br />\n肉類最後放<br />\n<br />\n洋蔥 薯仔煮到有少少透明就加醬汁 加水<br />\n關蓋煮10分鐘<br />\n再加肉 煮至熟透即可"},{"pid":"fbfd57c18b42dbfc88a3b8f2f68f2c4e9c089e12","tid":2258824,"uid":115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"咖哩汁的話 可以加一塊芝士<br />\n日式汁 可以加麵豉醬<br />\n<br />\n味道會提升"},{"pid":"70e36c793e1fb38c584bb44836aa3d28b2bd9e0e","tid":2258824,"uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"888c33a49a6495ebfcb9bff1788ab7d904708323","tid":2258824,"uid":164471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"西餐<br />\n煲熟d意粉/通粉再撈意粉醬<br />\n配料豐儉由人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1f959a4f16b77e7eabe79559752c39a592ca3f","tid":2258824,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"方便面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b4db5bd94bce6c378197c721fa3e98600b5957","tid":2258824,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"醃啲豬扒雞扒擺雪櫃，隨時攞出嚟煎/氣炸"},{"pid":"0d99cd405101a1bb54893e1cd06a16f5351f70e7","tid":2258824,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"888c33a49a6495ebfcb9bff1788ab7d904708323","tid":2258824,"uid":164471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cit